}}

==Ground transport==
[[Fram (agency)|Fram]] operates a local bus service between <U+00D8>rsta and Volda every half hour during the day and every hour during the evening. It stops at a bus stop seven minutes walk from the airport terminal. Paid parking, taxis and car rental are available at the airport. The airport is situated on the [[European route E39|E39]], five minutes driving from both <U+00D8>rsta and Volda.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://avinor.no/en/airport/orsta-volda-airport/to-and-from-the-airport/#!car-bus-and-taxi-973 |title=To and from the airport |publisher=[[Avinor]] |accessdate=12 January 2015}}</ref> 

